title: Video: Eddi Front – Superhero Style (Black Cab Sessions)
content:
Longtime CitR favourite Eddi Front has hooked up with the innovative video website Black Cab Sessions for this stunning rendition of EP track Superhero Style. Perfectly suited to her low-key, sultry musings, and the intimate environment providing a stark contrast to her classical good looks; her unique voice and songwriting talent ties the entire session together rather sweetly. Check it out below.

Black Cab Sessions – Eddi Front from Black Cab Sessions on Vimeo.
